### #FiveElements
p: The 5-elements serves as the foundation of the system. Air, Earth, Water, Fire, Ether. Water and earth are food, for all food consists of these two. Fire and air are the feeder, for by means of them man eats all food. Ether is the bowl, for all this is poured into the ether. Through the ether we call, through the ether we hear, through the ether we answer.
elements: Air, Earth, Water, Fire, Ether
set: #VedicThreeFoldAlgorithm.elemments

